summary: Diff updates PreMeditationPage, JournalPage, and ProgressPage to use StandardPageNav; PreMeditationPage also appears to remove the meditation type carousel, reintroduce the MeditationGuideStepper with a dismissible "More details" dialog, switch the active timer to MeditationTimerRing, and implement a sequential reflection step flow (mood → energy → note/favorite/save). No clear unrequested features are evidenced beyond these UX changes.
